reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This toy is well made and is very entertaining. My almost two year old sat and played with it for 20 minutes. And my 8 year old likes playing with it as well! Highly recommend this. Especially for younger kids. (That don’t put toys in their mouths.) The cars are small in size. So I wouldn’t recommend getting this unless the child will have no issues with putting the cars in their mouth.

reviews.reviewText: My 2 and 4 yr old boys love this ramp toy. Well made. I will definitely need to buy more of the cars though. They are small and get lost/misplaced easily. Comes with 5 and we are already down to only 2 cars since Christmas.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Don’t step on the cars
reviews.reviewText: Most toys last approximately 20 seconds & are then discarded for something else. My little boy can occupy close to 20 minutes playing with this one toy which is a miracle. The little cars make for excellent Antipersonnel mines & fit literally anywhere in your house.
